{"tid":2009830,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"處困境要務實，港獨不可行。 前港督衛奕信：香港勿成北京眼中威脅","createTime":"2020-05-10T04:46:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T07:05:19.000Z","uid":149978,"like":4,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"5b2e3ca554e1f9d65153a754ce26ed4257d406ff","tid":2009830,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T04:46:51.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】任內曾處理六四事件後香港信心危機的前港督衛奕信，在倫敦寓所接受本報專訪時表示，香港當前面對的社會撕裂、政府管治困難、中港關係緊張等問題，嚴峻程度遠不及1989年六四後的問題；香港人應保持樂觀務實，眼前困境並非無法解決。他強調，港獨訴求「完全不可行」，無論香港在殖民地時期或是現在，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">成功的要訣就是政治上不要被北京視為威脅。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n衛奕信並對香港年輕人從政提供意見。他說，近年香港年輕人熱心參與政治是好事，但香港主流社會必須保持務實態度，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">了解在現實條件限制下找出解決問題的方法。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170609/s00002/1496944481274\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170609%2Fs00002%2F1496944481274&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2FfpeBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=69a3a5dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170609%2Fs00002%2F1496944481274&h=72cc9621\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170609/s00002/1496944481274</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.tvbs.com.tw/world/735355\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvbs.com.tw%2Fworld%2F735355&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2FfpeBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=84f9fcd4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.tvbs.com.tw/world/735355</a>"},{"pid":"f8ee5de9dca68cfc2f20c7d237539099918f5aa4","tid":2009830,"uid":347987,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T04:47:57.000Z","msg":"英國挑戰西班牙無敵艦隊 都係不可行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae28b31aeaab2fe9d0f6bb346dbad2e87303fff5","tid":2009830,"uid":69707,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy